$ %LOCALAPPDATA%\Microsoft\WinGet\Packages

`%LOCALAPPDATA%\Microsoft\WinGet\Packages` is the user's *portable package root directory* for → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Local/Microsoft/WindowsApps/winget_exe[WinGet]
(see → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Local/Microsoft/WindowsApps/winget_exe#winget-info[`winget --info`]).

sa:
  `C:\Program Files\WinGet\Packages` and `C:\Program Files (x86)\WinGet\Packages`.
